title: Looking for an Oceania team for flex or solo/duo ranked
body:
I'm a season 8 s3.
I am an experienced player who is looking for people to play with that take the game seriously and want to climb ranked.
I play adc/top/jungle.
I can take feedback and instruction.
Add me and message me in lol TheSensation

replies.body: You can join my discord for team comp play/friend games if you like. https://discord.gg/QpMEaU
